Plan Your Switch to the Salesforce Data Model

Switching to the Salesforce data model ensures you get new and enhanced features for the Digital Insurance Platform in the future. You can harmonize Insurance Policy, Claim, and Group Benefits objects.

It's your choice to harmonize or not to harmonize, and when to do it. Before making the switch, analyze and prepare your org by recreating custom data, running migration scripts, updating reports and dashboards.
